.@FabrizioRomano on who he supports: &quot;I am a Watford fan!&quot;

&ldquo;I think everybody can see what Arteta is doing at the club. He&rsquo;s only been here for eight months. There were three competitions we could fight for. We got knocked out of the Europa League, unfairly in my view, but then we won the FA Cup and the Community Shield, which were well-deserved titles. <br />
&ldquo;More than that, though, it&rsquo;s about what he&rsquo;s created here &ndash; there&rsquo;s real positive energy in the dressing room, the players are happy and everyone is doing their bit. We&rsquo;re bringing through young players, which I think is really important for this club, because it&rsquo;s something that&rsquo;s always been done here. <br />
&ldquo;Mikel is the right person to get this club back to where it deserves to be, which I believe is in the Champions League, competing against the best teams in Europe.&rdquo;
